      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/aguti00/{size}/675_2.png",
      "created_at": "2022-06-22T01:09:37.196Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hello Alex, as always thanks for your answers, these are mine</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-English\" data-username=\"Alex\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"1617\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/48/1331_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>How were you feeling prior to the flu?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I felt strong and better than ever, even during the previous days I did PR on the most important climbs in my city.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-English\" data-username=\"Alex\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"1617\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/48/1331_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What was your TSB?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>47</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-English\" data-username=\"Alex\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"1617\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/48/1331_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Alex:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Were you feeling over trainined at all, meaning even though Jack plans are not super hard if you have a lot of stress or not getting good sleep it still might contribute. Understanding if stress was a contributer to getting ill partially changes the answer.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>not at all tired, I followed the rest days according to the plan and as you say it is very doable.</p>\n<p>the flu was because my daughter brought it from school.</p>\n<p>so far since last friday i don\u2019t do anything at all. I also took the opportunity to go on vacation for a few days with my wife taking advantage of the flu hahaha</p>\n<p>I think that if I feel good, next week I could start again, but I would like to know how and not lose all this training time, since I was going to PEAK and it was what I expected.</p>",
